  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK886">
<l>oṉṟāmai yoṉṟiyār kaṭpaṭi ṉeññāṉṟum</l>
<l>poṉṟāmai yoṉṟa laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If hatred arises among (one's) own people, it will be hardly possible (for one) to escape death.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
